<subSubSection pageId="26" pageNumber="305" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="26.[1380,2587,1827,2451]" pageId="26" pageNumber="305">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1382,1731,2261,2294]" pageId="26" pageNumber="305">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Near Threatened on The IUCN Red List. Royle’s Mountain Vole is presumed to be in significant decline because of large-scale habitat loss and close to being qualified as Vulnerable. Distribution is highly fragmented and covers only ¢.15,290 km?.
</paragraph>
